game.name: Car Toys Japan Season 2
game.description:
More fun and extra thrill are waiting for you in the second version of Car Toys Japan Season! Do you want to experience it by entering yourself in this brand new racing game? Join Car Toys Japan Season 2 and let the world tell that you are expert at parking any vehicle at any platform! The amazing fun environment of this loving racing puzzle will be enough to keep you engrossed for hours and hours. Make sure to put your hand-eye coordination and parking abilities to the test to complete all levels. 

There would be no time limits and no other restrictions to stop you from exploring your fun in your own style. There are multiple levels combined with different types of cars in different models to play through. Your objective in this cool html5 parking game is to complete different physics puzzles with the help of cars. Make sure to guide your vehicles to get over all the obstacles and complete each level with 3 stars rating. Your instant reaction will definitely help you to earn some bonus points. 

Click and move your car forward to get through a number of obstacles and obtain the maximum possible points in this car parking game! All the cute cars and other vehicles are seeking for the right spots during their fabulous fun adventure in Japan. You are surrounded by several competitors that want to capture the places available for parking on the playground. Be careful and capture all the designated parking spots while removing your rivals from the screen! Have car racing fun for free, no download required!
